        {
          "attributes":
          {
            "documentation": "@dev Returns an Ethereum Signed Message, created from a `hash`. This\nreplicates the behavior of the\n[`eth_sign`](https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC#eth_sign)\nJSON-RPC method.\n\n     * See `recover`.",
